snippet.title: Version 3.8 "Secret Summer Paradise" Trailer | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
"Welcome to the Veluriyam Mirage. I hope you can relax and enjoy some respite from your tiring journey."
It's as true as day that summer is the harbor for a momentary respite, an elysium for travelers to rest and recuperate.
What could go wrong when one seizes the fleeting holidays and plays to their heart's content?
